Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time for all instances of 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and subsequent 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Minimum time it takes from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' in cases where it leads to a 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' in cases where the declaration is resubmitted and approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total time it takes from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum time for a declaration to be resubmitted after being 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time for 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to be followed by any approval activity
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'", 'end': "activity == 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' or activity == 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' or activity == 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'", 'aggregation': 'average'}

Name: Total time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to the next 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' in cases of multiple rejections
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average waiting time to the 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' from the initial submission
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time it takes the 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to be done before 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' in the process flow leading to 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE' as a measure of correction time
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE'
